'''California''' was a location or possibly an organization in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. It was found on rectangular fore and aft markings on [[Buick]]s.<ref name="Star Wars: Rogue Squadron video game">[[Star Wars: Rogue Squadron (video game)|''Star Wars: Rogue Squadron'']]</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
[[Wikipedia:California|California]] is a real-world location in the [[Wikipedia:USA|United States of America]]. The game designers who programmed this into the game may have been simply drawing from this real-world area, as the plate matches those common on vehicles in the state.

